    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196790/extras/8b336d2d4fc42d43bc1ccb84a81664dd.avif?t=1740104107\" width=630 height=129 /></span>Fearbonding is a Yandere x Demon BL Horror Visual Novel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eat Fear</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tame the yandere</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweet and viscous like honey, that's how fear tastes to Hinata, a demon. True terror is hard to come by, so the day he meets Kosuke, his new goal is clear: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>He Needs to Tame This Terrifying Man.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Hinata in his harvest for fear, all without raising suspicion. Tread carefully as you try to get closer to the deranged Kosuke. Will you get to satisfy your hunger or will you be the one to get devoured?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196790/extras/16240229fe44e6e1d21421bd93271aa4.avif?t=1740104107\" width=630 height=129 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The first 4k words of the full game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >artstyle inspired by BL Horror Manga  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > a treat for anyone who likes horrifyingly toxic BL</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > a match made in hell</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196790/extras/34061dcbd56f1dce80f7cce07e941f49.avif?t=1740104107\" width=630 height=129 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hinata Kusumoto</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196790/extras/72998d5241665cb7b99783d08d9cf243.avif?t=1740104107\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kosuke Arima</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196790/extras/a5050dd2e77a2cc849f543a39d48b342.avif?t=1740104107\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p>",
